description:
Ongoing series written by Jonathan Luna and Sarah Vaughn. It was planned to be 12-issues long, however a few additional issues would be added later to bring the story to a fulfilling end.

Alex+Ada is a romantic Sci-Fi drama starring Alex, an office worker who is trying to forget about his last girlfriend and relationship, and Ada, a super-modern Tanaka X5 series android who is a birthday gift from his caring grandmother who already is in a somewhat satisfying relationship with a male android. While Alex is not really fond of the idea of dating a non-human person there is something about Ada.

Collected Editions

  • Alex + Ada Vol. 1 (#1-5)
  • Alex + Ada The Complete Collection: Deluxe Edition (#1-15)
  • Alex + Ada Vol. 2 (#6-10)
  • Alex + Ada Vol. 3 (#11-15)
name: Alex + Ada
